         <abstract id="aspace_732ef169c14ae5c39198cd0a76f1a5eb">Collection of miscellaneous scrapbooks and albums containing a variety of ephemera including trade cards, New Year's Day visiting cards, post cards, crests and monograms, cigarette cards, pressed flowers and plants, and clippings.</abstract>
         <origination label="Creator">
            <corpname source="local">
               <part localtype="agent_corporate_entity">Robert B. Haas Family Arts Library Special Collections</part>
            </corpname>
         </origination>
      </did>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_abf2d1890a2cf9db2f9f5800ee3a2589">
         <head>Content Description</head>
         <p>Collection of miscellaneous scrapbooks and albums containing a variety of ephemera including trade cards, New Year's Day visiting cards, post cards, crests and monograms, cigarette cards, pressed flowers and plants, and clippings.  An unused published wedding album, a cabinet photograph album, and several empty scrapbooks document late 19th-century printing and binding techniques.</p>
      </scopecontent>
      <arrangement id="aspace_b5d63e70d868214b1cf6bd4390e1689a">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>Arranged within two series: Series I. Filled scrapbooks and albums; Series II. Binding examples.</p>
      </arrangement>
